title: Door figurine

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a door figurine, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a perspective view of a door figurine in accordance with the invention;
FIG. 2 is a front elevation view of the door figurine shown in FIG. 1;
FIG. 3 is a rear elevation view of the door figurine shown in FIG. 1;
FIG. 4 is a left side elevation view of the door figurine shown in FIG. 1;
FIG. 5 is a right side elevation view of the door figurine shown in FIG. 1;
FIG. 6 is a top plan view of the door figurine shown in FIG. 1; and,
FIG. 7 is a bottom plan view of the door figurine shown in FIG. 1.
The dashed lines shown in FIGS. 1, 2, 4 and 5 are for illustration purposes only and form no part of the claimed design.
